title: STUNNING UNIT IN LUXURY FLATIRON BRICKELL!
posting_body: ['Enjoy stunning views from this corner unit at The Brickell Flatiron.', '2 Beds, 2.5 Baths + Den, top-of-the-line Miele appliances, Italian doors, glass-enclosed showers, 9’ foot ceilings and a wraparound balcony.', 'Brickell Flatiron is a full-service building featuring a stunning Sky Pool on the 64th floor with 360-degree-views of Miami and Biscayne Bay, a Fitness Room, Wellness Center and Spa, amongst other amenities.', "The newest of Ugo Colombo's iconic buildings is centrally and idyllically located in the heart of Brickell, with easy access to restaurants, shopping, downtown Miami, Coconut Grove, Miami Beach and the Miami International Airport.", 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
